<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <title>HCMS Encrichment Fair</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="${static_url}/static/css/default.css"/>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="${static_url}/static/css/main.css"/>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="title">
                <a href="/"><img src="${static_url}/static/img/HCMSPhoto.png"></a>
                <h1>Harper's Choice - Enrichment Fair</h1>
            </div>
            <div class="nav">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="body">
            <div class="bodynav">
                <h1>Welcome all to the HCMS Enrichment Fair!</h1>

                <a id="submit_link" href="/code">Click here to submit a code!</a>

                <h3>By clicking the link above, you can submit codes you find from viewing presentations to
                enter a large raffle to win prizes like an AMC, Coldstone, and Burger King gift card! <br>The more
                presentations and codes you view and submit, you have a higher chance of winning an item! The public leaderboard
                will be in the main lobby.<br>

                If you have any technical difficulties with the website, find someone with a walkie talkie or a Event Organizer nametag so
                we can get you back in the game as soon as possible.<br>

                <br>For rules, we please ask you to not submit inappropriate names. By doing so, we will ban you from participating in the raffle.<br>

                    <strong style="color: red; font-size:24pt;">Also, avoid using a incognito/private browser, and it may harm the ability for the site to recognize you and give you codes.</strong>
                    <br>
                    Have a great night!
                </h3>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <footer class="footer">
            <p>Made by D.J. Figueroa</p>
    </footer>
